{"tid":1612303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1，手足中槍事件，大家漏咗啲嘢","createTime":"2019-10-02T08:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:54.000Z","uid":116981,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e3d95228431f9f4181fb83945c67e401f9a0ae","tid":1612303,"uid":116981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"1.一開始支槍唔係指向手足，係手足發現黑警指向其他人，諗住救人<br />\n<br />\n2.開槍後係冇黑警上前睇手足情況，試問係槍聲之下，黑槍冇可能唔知開咗槍，<strong>而開槍既黑警冇可能唔知佢射中咗人，但呢個情況下冇人救援，黑警根本想拖到手足失救</strong><br />\n<br />\n3.暫時見到片段入邊，我肯定唔到開槍黑警究竟係開槍後有冇留低係現場，定係即時離開現場？"},{"pid":"0ad745b52e9ac41e4dcf05e929be7a4a789347ac","tid":1612303,"uid":205555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa284e5097632d8f09b4ac9c1dcc486bf247896d","tid":1612303,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"有五分鐘係由得佢流血冇黑警理過，就算訓係度狂叫救命"},{"pid":"aa692d76766578f83b6683e4187290204837d7ce","tid":1612303,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dQ01zD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dQ01zD.png&h=233686df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bca7a86cc22bffbec00150033eb2c6f7bab2f60","tid":1612303,"uid":116981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36cb75f0c59da77f02dd5abd732406fead5f327","tid":1612303,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"黑警直頭想佢死啦<br />\n死咗咪可以直接毀屍滅跡死無對證<br />\n831都係咁處理架啦<br />\n新屋嶺都係咁處理架啦"}]}